{"tid":1895894,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"手頭上有  “足夠”  口罩嘅你請入一入嚟","createTime":"2020-02-24T20:58:16.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-25T15:32:47.000Z","uid":232671,"like":21,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"fd2c7d57a22bf7ec71af6628c1506e2e92ca81e1","tid":1895894,"uid":232671,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-24T20:58:16.000Z","msg":"純粹提醒<br />\n唔好諗住呢排供應多咗，而自己手上有貨就用得爽手咗<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/sosick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n歐洲啱啱先開始爆，照計唔會咁快完，隨時要捱到9月<br />\n<br />\n大家請諗長遠啲，行多一步<br />\n有貨買貨，冇貨請積極考慮用豬咀<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />堅好用<br />\n<br />\nBTW, 大家買罩時請特別注意，以免中招：<br />\n1要預先俾錢<br />\n2需要你提供敏感個人資料（例如身份證）<br />\n3用黃色經濟圈/香港製造為名做推廣<br />\n<br />\n自己香港自己救<br />\n<br />\n光復香港 時代革命"},{"pid":"ad1acf43ea59ed102996c77fa60cb0ba2d1477be","tid":1895894,"uid":232671,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-24T21:36:17.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"e6e5bc2b239f95bdc9b40cfb090b43db5fc84faf","tid":1895894,"uid":244832,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-24T21:44:10.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"0757db22411891592e986e4d860e5860c6d16f07","tid":1895894,"uid":117422,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-24T22:06:51.000Z","msg":"9月<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/dust.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"571ce04569765f6f467d06f3c631ea2edb15ce56","tid":1895894,"uid":59920,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-24T22:08:06.000Z","msg":"等買MIHK<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1b8f3d21e8b68345c279eec7f039ac8b0e7310ea","tid":1895894,"uid":149487,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-24T22:08:20.000Z","msg":"9月<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" cla